$$ 
$$ ;for z-only gradients:
$$ ;gpz1: 50% for C-13, 70% for N-15
$$ ;gpz2: 30%
$$ ;gpz3: 40.1% for C-13, 50.1% for N-15
$$ 
$$ ;use gradient files:   
$$ ;gpnam1: SMSQ10.100
$$ ;gpnam2: SMSQ10.100
$$ ;gpnam3: SMSQ10.100
